[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/Mary1.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: Calm down rose.
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/Rose2.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose: you seem like a bad guy, what are your motivations?!
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/HeartHoarder1.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Hmm... my goal? to harvest your sick and twisted world.
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/Rose3.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose: Excuse me?! Who do you think you are, calling our world sick?!
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/Mary2.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: That's not true...
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/HeartHoarder2.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Such indignation, little ones. Your world thrives on conflict. Greed. Betrayal. It's rotting from the inside out.
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/Mary3.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: Even if what you said is true... How would this cruel invasion of yours solve anything?
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level3Outro/HeartHoarder3.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Well... before I continue, let me introduce myself. I am what others call the "Heart Hoarder", although my real name, I do not remember.
